This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the use of neural networks to model population dynamics. It may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks in an evolutionary context. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the development of intelligent systems. The paper also touches upon the topic of coevolution, which could place it under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
